00:04:27.490 --> 00:04:31.079
In the actual length of these arrows are gonna be about the same length as our bow itself

00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:36.510
so just lay the skewer over top find the distance and then break it off near the bottom and to help them walk into the

00:04:36.510 --> 00:04:37.229
bowstring a little bit better

